{"tid":1318952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係沙田人，我有野想講","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T05:30:20.000Z","uid":230184,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c27d32787143fb604ab0c0da162da0e33e826c4b","tid":1318952,"uid":230184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"住係沙田差不多成十年<br />\n好耐都冇見到甘熱鬧場面<br />\n我指市民遊行，令沙田熱鬧起來<br />\n而唔係警察暴力清場果種熱鬧<br />\n好多人話破壞左好多設施<br />\n好多設施可以維修好<br />\n但人與人之間既矛盾好難一時三刻回復當時<br />\n岩就岩，錯左就係錯左<br />\n有咩唔岩可以傾可以講，但連傾聽既機會都冇仲有咩好講<br />\n<br />\n對於琴日新城市廣場場面，我唔識評論，我只可以講，有岩都有錯，最緊要安全回到家中<br />\n<br />\n最後香港人一定要加油，爭取自己得到既野<br />\n我們一起攜手走下去<br />\n<br />\n區區遍地開花<br />\n世界遍地開花<br />\n人民遍地開花<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uTe2jxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuTe2jxB.png&h=a92de528&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dcf9baeb879b2c85eba780e7560406c09398249","tid":1318952,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yziVEtq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyziVEtq.png&h=7c6764ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41a67c0bb4a30464734842afebb81f9e4f829d9d","tid":1318952,"uid":248275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？<br />\n好似講左好多野，但又唔覺得你講左野<br />\n究竟你有冇講野？"},{"pid":"aa9de85eba01cea500706b9ed3fc470f9c72dc23","tid":1318952,"uid":219079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41a67c0bb4a30464734842afebb81f9e4f829d9d","tid":1318952,"uid":248275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？<br />\n好似講左好多野，但又唔覺得你講左野<br />\n究竟你有冇講野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"係囉到底up乜"}]}